---
title: Sesame Shrimp with Ginger-Green Onion Rice and Crispy Green Beans
description: Tossing shrimp in a sweet hoisin glaze creates delicious caramelization in the pan. By stirring a bit of ginger and green onion into the rice, we’re infusing it with fragrant aromatics. These quick tricks make for a super flavourful 30-minute stir-fry!
